      "content": "Your description of feeling like your core has vanished is a profound and terrifying experience that often signals a deep crisis in identity and purpose. When the creative spark or the emotional engine that once defined you disappears, the remaining self can feel incredibly hollow and disconnected from reality. It is completely valid to feel that there is no one left to answer the call, even though the pain you feel right now is a testament to your past capacity to feel and create.",
      "source": "target",
